@startuml
actor User
participant "Frontend (Province Page)" as FE
participant "API Server" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> FE: Open /province/{id}
FE -> API: GET /api/provinces/{id}
API -> DB: Select province by id
DB --> API: Province row
API --> FE: Province JSON

FE -> API: GET /api/provinces/{id}/summary
API -> DB: Count stories/herbs/villages\n(+pending counts)
DB --> API: Summary
API --> FE: Summary JSON

FE -> API: GET /api/stories?provinceId={id}
API -> DB: Select approved stories
DB --> API: Story list
API --> FE: Stories JSON

FE -> API: GET /api/herbs?provinceId={id}
API -> DB: Select approved herbs
DB --> API: Herb list
API --> FE: Herbs JSON

FE -> API: GET /api/villages?provinceId={id}
API -> DB: Select approved villages
DB --> API: Village list
API --> FE: Villages JSON

FE --> User: Render dashboard tabs + media
@enduml
